✔ Easy upgrades

✔ Easy rollback

✔ Reduced YAML duplication

✔ Standardized deployments

✔ Easy maintenance

✔ Increased productivity

✔ Reduced human errors

==========================================
Interview Answer
==========================================

In our project, we use Helm to deploy applications across Development, QA, and Production environments. We maintain a single reusable Helm Chart and use separate values files for each environment. This avoids maintaining multiple YAML files, simplifies upgrades and rollbacks, ensures consistent deployments, and significantly improves productivity.